Title: Law & Order: Special Victims Unit
Actors: Mariska Hargitay, Ice-T, Richard Belzer, Dann Florek, Christopher Meloni, Danny Pino, Kelli Giddish, Mary Stuart Masterson, Dean Winters, Adam Beach, Tamara Tunie, Michaela Mcmanus, Michelle Hurd, Stephanie March, B.D. Wong, Diane Neal
Plot: This show delves into the dark side of the New York underworld as the detectives of a new elite force, the Special Victims Unit, investigate and prosecute various sexually oriented crimes, while trying to balance the effects of the investigation on their own lives.
